      <title>特朗普选择万斯助手詹姆斯·布雷德负责立法事务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/trump-picks-vance-aide-james-braid-to-run-legislative-affairs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着新一届政府政治运作领导层的形成，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普任命竞选搭档 JD 万斯的高级助理詹姆斯·布雷德为白宫立法事务办公室的负责人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/trump-picks-vance-aide-james-braid-to-run-legislative-affairs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 00:08:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普誓言对中国、墨西哥、加拿大征收边境关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/trump-vows-to-hit-china-mexico-canada-with-tariffs-over-border</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他将对来自中国的商品征收 10% 的额外关税，对来自墨西哥和加拿大的所有产品征收 25% 的关税，称这些征税对于打击跨越美国边境的移民和非法毒品是必要的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/trump-vows-to-hit-china-mexico-canada-with-tariffs-over-border</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 23:55:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Meta、TikTok、谷歌抨击澳大利亚禁止 16 岁以下用户使用社交媒体</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/meta-tiktok-google-slam-australia-s-under-16-social-media-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[包括 Meta、TikTok 和谷歌在内的全球科技巨头严厉批评了澳大利亚禁止 16 岁以下儿童访问社交媒体平台的立法，这为政府本周试图推动议会通过该法案的政策之争奠定了基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/meta-tiktok-google-slam-australia-s-under-16-social-media-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 23:23:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国向基辅投下更多风暴阴影，斯塔默承诺提供支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/uk-sends-kyiv-more-storm-shadows-as-starmer-pledges-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，英国政府最近向乌克兰提供了数十枚“风暴阴影”巡航导弹，这是英国首相基尔·斯塔默上任以来首次向乌克兰提供该导弹。基尔·斯塔默已承诺将继续支持乌克兰对俄罗斯的战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/uk-sends-kyiv-more-storm-shadows-as-starmer-pledges-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 22:22:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列和真主党即将达成协议 但袭击仍在继续</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/israel-and-hezbollah-on-the-cusp-of-deal-as-attacks-continue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据官员和知情人士透露，尽管双方仍在继续互相发射炮弹和火箭弹，但以色列和真主党已接近签署停火协议，该协议可能在未来几天内达成。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/israel-and-hezbollah-on-the-cusp-of-deal-as-attacks-continue</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 22:10:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前 Wamco 首席信息官 Ken Leech 因交易分配计划被指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/ken-leech-sued-by-sec-over-alleged-cherry-picking-scheme</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西方资产管理公司 (Western Asset Management Co.) 前联席首席投资官肯·利奇 (Ken Leech) 周一被美国当局指控不当将交易分配给优先客户，这对这位曾经的明星交易员来说是一个戏剧性的转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/ken-leech-sued-by-sec-over-alleged-cherry-picking-scheme</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 21:53:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊姆兰·汗支持者在伊斯兰堡举行游行，却遭遇致命暴力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/imran-khan-s-supporters-march-to-islamabad-demanding-his-release</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一晚间，要求释放巴基斯坦被监禁的前总理伊姆兰汗的抗议者进入首都伊斯兰堡，挫败了总理谢赫巴兹谢里夫政府镇压全国性示威活动的努力，引发了暴力事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/imran-khan-s-supporters-march-to-islamabad-demanding-his-release</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 18:53:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>司法部将撤销华盛顿和佛罗里达对特朗普的起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/doj-formally-moves-to-drop-trump-2020-obstruction-case-in-dc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国司法部终止了对唐纳德·特朗普的刑事指控，这标志着对这位前总统的特别联邦起诉已经结束。特朗普的连任确保了他不会在白宫受到指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/doj-formally-moves-to-drop-trump-2020-obstruction-case-in-dc</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 18:26:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚预算因结构性赤字而大幅超支</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/australia-budget-blow-out-seen-as-structural-deficit-takes-hold</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德勤经济研究所 (Deloitte Access Economics) 表示，澳大利亚的预算赤字可能会超出预期，与前几年的情况相反，当时铁矿石价格高企带来了巨额收入提升，最终使账面转为盈余。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/australia-budget-blow-out-seen-as-structural-deficit-takes-hold</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默面临因复工计划引发争议的风险，企业警告将裁员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/starmer-s-budget-pains-grow-as-welfare-push-hit-by-jobs-warning</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 提出计划，通过让更多人就业来减少福利支出，与此同时，企业警告称，由于税收增加，他们将进行裁员，因此他冒着再次就工党政府备受争议的首份预算展开斗争的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/starmer-s-budget-pains-grow-as-welfare-push-hit-by-jobs-warning</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 10:52:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
